ka 2010 a cavilj- pinakalevavan ta “文化勳章”

ka 2010 a cavilj- pinakalevavan ta “北海道功勞獎別獎”

ka 2010 a cavilj- pinakalevavan tua masan ta鵡川町特別名譽町民

ka 2010 a cavilj- pinakalevavan ta “鵡川町特別功勞獎”

